text: Kuyavian-Pomeranian (), officially called Poland's 2nd European Parliament constituency (), is a European Parliament constituency in Poland. It represents the Kuyavian-Pomeranian Voivodeship. It was created in 2004. ==References== Category:European Parliament constituencies in Poland Category:Kuyavian-Pomeranian Voivodeship
